{"tid":726512,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"菲律賓市長把販毒疑犯遊街   被狙擊暗殺","createTime":"2018-07-02T12:41:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-02T13:25:04.000Z","uid":79563,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"13804adceb31c3fe75d171052975b86a477ae272","tid":726512,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:41:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://newsstatic.rthk.hk/images/mfile_1404777_1_L_20180702173930.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnewsstatic.rthk.hk%2Fimages%2Fmfile_1404777_1_L_20180702173930.jpg&h=480bbc14&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n菲律賓塔納武安市市長哈里里出席市政府升旗儀式時被暗殺，懷疑是與哈里里的強硬掃毒立場有關。<br />\n<br />\n哈里里早上與過百名政府🇨🇳🇨🇳人員🇨🇳🇨🇳與地方代表，在市政府唱國歌期間遭到狙擊手槍殺。哈里里身邊的民眾尖叫及爭相走避，哈里里的保鑣向子彈射來的一處山頭開火，暫時未有人被捕。<br />\n<br />\n哈里里兩年前要求販毒疑犯遊街，一度被人權組織批評。不過哈里里亦曾經捲入涉毒罪案，哈里里否認涉案。"},{"pid":"4abd6193c1e976aa06aff151d10fee7f72511610","tid":726512,"uid":3457,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:43:38.000Z","msg":"菲律賓總統咁撚惡d毒犯都仲敢聊 真係嫌命長 以為自己係墨西哥"},{"pid":"36945fb1512c6a014a390541072ce989b7ce24ff","tid":726512,"uid":153811,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:43:42.000Z","msg":"政治清算屈人毒販<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"43677c479d4b65efcfe002cc3ff97fa573a510ad","tid":726512,"uid":92758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"link?"},{"pid":"b3b4213745533ffeec3d83278eb56436b866d4e0","tid":726512,"uid":79563,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"43677c479d4b65efcfe002cc3ff97fa573a510ad","tid":726512,"uid":92758,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:43:49.000Z","msg":"link?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-02T12:44:49.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1404777-20180702.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1404777-20180702.htm&d=RmGgjlo2L4VoqaZYw